.START 

First Capital Holdings Corp. said it called for the redemption of 5.1 million shares of $2.0625 cumulative convertible preferred at $26.65 a share. 

The preferred is convertible until 5 p.m. EDT Nov. 9 at $8.40 a share (equivalent to 2.9762 shares of common for each share of preferred).
Cash will be paid for fractional shares. 

The financial services holding company declined to comment on why it was calling for the redemption. 

